data.description: INVESTOR ALERT!!!!!Three Bedroom, One Bath Bungalow right off of Landis Avenue.  There are natural hardwood floors throughout with an enclosed front porch.  There is also a living room with wood burning fireplace, dining room with wood tray ceilings, kitchen and morning room.  The home was built in 1923 with a lot of original fixtures, built ins, etc.  There is also a pull down attic that is floored and can be counted as a bonus room.   The rear of the property has a detached barn or garage that is quite big.  The property is in need of some TLC but has a lot of vintage charm.  Being sold "AS IS".   Book your tour today!!!
